Title: Putting photos in order
Description: Choose which of the two photos is more complex
Answer.criteria: many of the pictures had strikingly different colors in them, and this played a role. However, depth and texture probably played a bigger role. For example, if the color black was present to some degree in both pictures, but one picture had the color black due to highly varying degrees of depth, then I would consider that one to be more complex. Pictures that seemed more uniform in what type of thing the picture consisted of, despite varying degrees of color, seemed less complex to me. For example, if leaves had a variety of colors, but the other pictures had a variety of materials, such as straw against a background of another material, the picture with more types of materials seem more complex.
